title: Bobby Offers Eddie $100 To Sell His Soul + Favorite 90’s Things Draft + Eddie ‘Tests’ Toilet Paper
itunes:title: Bobby Offers Eddie $100 To Sell His Soul + Favorite 90’s Things Draft + Eddie ‘Tests’ Toilet Paper
description:
Bobby and Eddie have a dumb debate that leads with Bobby offering to buy Eddie’s soul. Does Eddie buy into it? We draft our favorite things from the 90’s in today’s draft! Plus, Bobby gives Eddie three different types of toilet paper to try and see if he can tell any differences!
